      <title>日本的区域银行股票对联盟的期望提高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/japan-s-regional-bank-shares-jump-on-expectations-for-alliances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本的区域银行对行业整合的乐观情绪激起了人们的乐观，其中一位贷方正在考虑购买同行的股份，而其他贷方则报告了计划企业联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/japan-s-regional-bank-shares-jump-on-expectations-for-alliances</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 03:12:10 GMT</pubDate>
